<LP>
   DETROIT -- General Motors Acceptance Corp., the financial
arm of General Motors Corp., said it will exercise its option
to redeem on June 1, 1990, all of its 12% debentures
outstanding due to mature June 1, 2005. The debentures will
be redeemed at 102% of their principal amount.
